Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来有请Edel Rose的一条新选手登场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只要小新能发挥出平时的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就足够逆转Schwarz了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那套服装不是我设计的服装啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得那套服装好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我的话  能绽放出更多的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,小新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,琉铱…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧  新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在舞台上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那我的表演呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.52,Up,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs55\fad(700,1)\3c&H7368E1&}一条新  0克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,新君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快送他去医务室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的是组合对决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,由Schwarz Rose的新生The Shuffle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,和Edel Rose的Edel Rose Seven Stars登场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,医生说他只是累到睡着了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,过会儿要送他去医院做一下精密检查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才真的是新君吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,确实就像换了个人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,新  那些招式你是从哪儿学来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是过去的资料中未曾出现过的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,新刚进Edel Rose的那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,都不敢相信那是他第一次表演Prism Show
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.74,Prism Jump 红色,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}新无限拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.74,Prism Jump 红色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur5\fad(300,300)}Shin Mugen Hug
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,难道他不是人类?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我  谁来把我从这里救出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.22,Up,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs55\fad(700,1)\3c&H7368E1&}交响曲妇产科医院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…刚出生时的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,能生下你真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,名字就叫新
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,汉字是新生的「新」字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面  小新
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是奶奶的家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来要去哪个世界旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,流星?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来以前好像有见过  又好像没见过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不是在做梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,铃音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里  救我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,铃音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,新  在这种地方睡着是会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  新  快起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,幼稚园的游艺会?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我的动作做反了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好  茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs65}茄子!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小学的开学典礼  好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是加入足球俱乐部的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是修学旅行  我们去了日光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,上了中学  功课一下子变难了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,社团的大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一上场就输掉  很不甘心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,初三  作为应考生开始去补习班了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,琉铱君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真是宛如隔日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,铃音?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是铃音对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是我  闪音!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Over The Rainbow的演唱会  真的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,颜色在慢慢恢复…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Edel Rose的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,雪之丞同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,玲央
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,港同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,翔同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候根本没想到能和他们相处得这么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs65}多亏了幸司前辈的特训  我能够跳出Prism Jump了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:48.20,Prism Jump 红色,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}红线 夏之恋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好心动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.50,Prism Jump 粉色,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}蜂蜜之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.50,Prism Jump 粉色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur5\fad(300,300)}Hachimitsu Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,将你内心深处的思念毫无隐藏地挖出来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,内心深处的思念…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,力量在慢慢恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.16,Prism Jump 红色,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}新无限拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.16,Prism Jump 红色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur5\fad(300,300)}Shin Mugen Hug
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是最能绽放出Prism的光芒的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一条新  Prism Show开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我做梦也想不到自己能站在Rose Party的舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我有话想对大家说!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.38,pink,,0,0,0,,『什么~』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,想找到你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,把好多的爱传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:54.10,Prism Jump 红色,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}Over the Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都因为我的Jump而露出了笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,铃音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你没有杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是圣诞演出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,「戏剧性的LOVE」 大家都很喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,力量…力量在不断涌上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点就能完全复活了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在能和我来场Prism Show吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,和琉铱君一起跳舞  不是梦吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:53.21,Prism Jump 粉色,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}百分百 纯洁之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:53.21,Prism Jump 粉色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur5\fad(300,300)}100% Pure Pure Arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs65}这不就和那个时候一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:56.70,Prism Jump 粉色,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}漫天飞舞 恋爱之花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:56.70,Prism Jump 粉色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur5\fad(300,300)}Hirahira Hiraku Koi no Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs65}住手  铃音  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:10:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs65}我再也不想回到那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,想再看一回你的Prism Show
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs65}为什么  为什么要把我从黑暗中救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs65}有什么目的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,琉铱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.77,Prism Jump 紫色,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}轻声密语的月色神秘天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.77,Prism Jump 紫色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur5\fad(300,300)}Sasayaki no Lunamystic Heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不想回到那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,明星光斑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx55\fscy55}Star Splash
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Prism Jump… 跳不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,再柔软灵活一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候我突然跳不出Prism Jump了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是多亏了雪之丞同学的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.79,Prism Jump 红色,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}Prism Rush
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,三连跳
