Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,让大家见识一下Edel Rose史上最棒的Prism Show吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:20:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别太勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你就安心休息吧
